column5: WITH ServiceVersionCounts AS (SELECT I.SID, MS.version, COUNT(MS.version) AS frequency FROMInternetService I JOIN ModelServices MS ON I.SID = MS.SID JOIN BaseModel B ON MS.bmid = B.bmid GROUP BY I.SID, MS.version), RankedVersions AS ( SELECT SID, version, frequency, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY SID ORDER BY frequency DESC) AS rn FROMServiceVersionCounts) SELECT SID,version AS most_frequent_version FROM RankedVersions WHERE rn = 1;

WITH ServiceVersionCounts AS (SELECT SID, version, COUNT(*) AS VersionCount FROM ModelServices GROUP BY SID, version), RankedServiceVersions AS (SELECT SID, version, VersionCount, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY SID ORDER BY VersionCount DESC) AS RankNum FROM ServiceVersionCounts) SELECT SID, version AS MostFrequentVersion FROM RankedServiceVersions WHERE RankNum = 1;

column5: SELECT MS.SID FROM ModelServices MS JOIN BaseModel B ON MS.bmid = B.bmid JOIN AgentCreator AC ON B.creator_uid = AC.uid JOIN User U ON AC.uid = U.uid WHERE U.username = 'user_iuwrh' GROUP BY MS.SID HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT B.BMID) = (SELECT COUNT(BMID) FROM BaseModel B_sub JOIN AgentCreator AC_sub ON B_sub.creator_uid = AC_sub.uid JOIN User U_sub ON AC_sub.uid = U_sub.uid WHERE U_sub.username = 'user_iuwrh');

SELECT T1.SID FROM ModelServices AS T1 WHERE T1.BMID IN (SELECT T3.BMID FROM User AS T2 JOIN AgentCreator AS T_AC ON T2.UID = T_AC.UID JOIN BaseModel AS T3 ON T_AC.UID = T3.creator_uid WHERE T2.username = 'user_iuwrh') GROUP BY T1.SID HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT T1.BMID) = (SELECT COUNT(T4.BMID) FROM User AS T5 JOIN AgentCreator AS T_AC_sub ON T5.UID = T_AC_sub.UID JOIN BaseModel AS T4 ON T_AC_sub.UID = T4.creator_uid WHERE T5.username = 'user_iuwrh');
